{"tid":205004,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"是日三餐 17/04/2017","createTime":"2017-04-17T12:50:19.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-17T15:12:14.000Z","uid":18117,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"7009e6f2126b042a3da754a6b5c30711c030010a","tid":205004,"uid":18117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-17T12:50:19.000Z","msg":"胃潰瘍好得7788 終於有番啲胃口食野<br />\n本身已經瘦底 依家病完得番100磅鬆啲<br />\n想試下係度記錄低自己每日食過既野<br />\n順便提醒自己每日要食多啲<br />\n<br />\n#早餐<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/04/17/204333_d2adecc715ad273426ba3eec247bcc64.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F04%2F17%2F204333_d2adecc715ad273426ba3eec247bcc64.jpg&h=f51a9056&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n#午餐<br />\n一人一個兩餸飯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/04/17/204532_39fef9bf7f1f55037f10cf9251a6856c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F04%2F17%2F204532_39fef9bf7f1f55037f10cf9251a6856c.jpg&h=63f79257&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n#晚餐 <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/04/17/204634_5ce6ff34d58d1cbbf3277aef781ccc26.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F04%2F17%2F204634_5ce6ff34d58d1cbbf3277aef781ccc26.jpg&h=b47a6f26&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n諗住食粟米六粒飯 <br />\n點知忍唔到口叫左香茅豬<br />\n仲飲左杯凍野 好罪惡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b5bce71597dfd35bf899cdbdecf61e04119d5de","tid":205004,"uid":56716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-17T13:00:59.000Z","msg":"今日ok喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n無咁清淡了，保重身體呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e0d2030a3ccb296c5bac1c8cd4d376e60c7ae6eb","tid":205004,"uid":18117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-17T13:05:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>今日ok喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n無咁清淡了，保重身體呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n多謝吉野妹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7991a0c74d5dfcb0f01507c232261282eb6d9c20","tid":205004,"uid":71166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-17T13:30:00.000Z","msg":"pan pan<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c9b1efc80900f2d50b2e7667bba9c7600ad1324","tid":205004,"uid":18117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-17T14:06:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>pan pan<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n肥仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d0295b54ac67836a53c32af3f8afecb32b569f37","tid":205004,"uid":72872,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-17T14:56:55.000Z","msg":"早餐杯野係咩黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a2670c6b0124cb64ff4463985b99c43e7c8ed49b","tid":205004,"uid":18117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-17T15:12:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>早餐杯野係咩黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n菊花 依兩日打得多邊爐 要清下熱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}